METADATAEXTENSION.NAME: SQL_Query
METADATAEXTENSION.VALUE: call DWH_TOOL.LOAD_INSERT(' WITH SRC as ( SELECT loadudbm.md5( DECODE(SRC.MEASURE, NULL, ''#NULL#'', TO_CHAR(SRC.MEASURE))||''|''|| DECODE(SRC.ACTION, NULL, ''#NULL#'', TO_CHAR(SRC.ACTION))||''|''|| DECODE(SRC.CHANNEL_CODE, NULL, ''#NULL#'', TO_CHAR(SRC.CHANNEL_CODE))||''|''|| DECODE(SRC.INITIATIVE_CODE, NULL, ''#NULL#'', TO_CHAR(SRC.INITIATIVE_CODE))||''|''|| DECODE(SRC.ADVERTISING_DESIGN_CODE, NULL, ''#NULL#'', TO_CHAR(SRC.ADVERTISING_DESIGN_CODE))||''|''|| DECODE(SRC.CONTACT_TYPE_CODE, NULL, ''#NULL#'', TO_CHAR(SRC.CONTACT_TYPE_CODE))||''|''|| DECODE(SRC.CAMPAIGN_SUB_PROGRAM_CODE, NULL, ''#NULL#'', TO_CHAR(SRC.CAMPAIGN_SUB_PROGRAM_CODE))) AS HK , current_timestamp as LDTS , ''KAMPMETA'' AS RSRC , x''00000000000000000000000000000000'' AS HF , SRC.MEASURE, SRC.ACTION, SRC.SUB_CAMPAIGN_NAME, SRC.CHANNEL_CODE, SRC.INITIATIVE_CODE, SRC.ADVERTISING_DESIGN_CODE, SRC.CONTACT_TYPE_CODE, SRC.COST_UNIT, SRC.COST_CENTER, SRC.CAMPAIGN_SUB_PROGRAM_CODE, SRC.EDITION_PLANNED, SRC.DELIVERY_LETTERSHOP, SRC.CAMPAIGN_FIXED_COST, SRC.EDITION_FINAL, SRC.PARTNER_CONTRIBUTION, SRC.CONTACT_DATE, SRC.SELECTION_DATE FROM METADATAEXTENSION.NAME: SQL_Query
METADATAEXTENSION.VALUE: call DWH_TOOL.LOAD_INSERT(' WITH SRC as ( SELECT loadudbm.md5() AS HK , current_timestamp as LDTS , ''KAMPMETA'' AS RSRC , x''00000000000000000000000000000000'' AS HF , SRC.USERNAME, SRC.FIRST_LASTNAME, SRC.PERMISSIONS FROM KAMPDB_R.KAMPMETA_USER_VW_R SRC ), TGT as ( select tgt.USER_VW_HK HK, tgt.USER_VW_HF HF, from ( select tgt.*, row_number() over (partition by USER_VW_HK order by ldts desc) as version from KAMPDB_HA.KAMPMETA_USER_VW_HA tgt with ur ) tgt where version = 1 ) SELECT SRC.* FROM SRC LEFT JOIN TGT ON WHERE 1=1 AND ( TGT.HK IS NULL OR (TGT.HK IS NOT NULL AND SRC.HF!=TGT.HF) ) WITH UR' , 'KAMPDB_HA.CODIAC_USER_VW_HA', ?); COMMIT;
